# 🚀 CodePilot AI

CodePilot AI is an AI-powered software engineering assistant that understands GitHub repositories using semantic search and vector embeddings.

Instead of keyword search, CodePilot AI indexes an entire repository into vector embeddings, enabling developers to ask natural language questions about any codebase.

---

## ✨ Features

### ✅ Milestone 1
- Clone any public GitHub repository
- REST API using FastAPI
- Automatic repository storage

### ✅ Milestone 2
- Recursive repository scanning
- Ignore unnecessary directories
- Filter supported source code files
- Extract file metadata
- Repository parsing API

### ✅ Milestone 3
- Read repository source code
- Split large files into chunks
- Generate embeddings using SentenceTransformers
- Store embeddings in FAISS
- Semantic code search
- Search API

---

## 🏗️ Project Architecture

```
GitHub Repository
        │
        ▼
Clone Repository
        │
        ▼
Repository Parser
        │
        ▼
Read File Contents
        │
        ▼
Chunk Source Code
        │
        ▼
Generate Embeddings
        │
        ▼
FAISS Vector Store
        │
        ▼
Semantic Search
```

