│
├── app/
│   ├── api/
│   ├── core/
│   ├── schemas/
│   └── services/
│
├── repos/
│
├── vector_store/
│
├── requirements.txt
│
└── main.py
```

---

## 🚀 Getting Started

Install dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Run the backend

```bash
uvicorn main:app --reload
```

Open Swagger

```
http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs
```

